title: open web
extract: Definition of: open Web (1) The public side of the Web. There are parts of the Web that are public and viewable by everyone and others that are private. See surface Web and deep Web. (2) The countries that do not restrict their citizens from viewing content on the Web.
extract_html: Definition of: open Web (1) The public side of the Web. There are parts of the Web that are public and viewable by everyone and others that are private. See surface Web and deep Web. (2) The countries that do not restrict their citizens from viewing content on the Web.
